<P>
Brief 
</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
BUSING; SEATTLE (WA) -- SCHOOLS; INITIATIVES -- WASHINGTON (STATE); SEATTLE 
(WA) -- ELECTIONS; SCHOOL INTEGRATION 
</P>
