<HEADLINE>
<P>
SAN DIEGO INDUSTRY NOTES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Aquasearch has entered a letter of intent to form a joint venture with Pecoff 
Bros. Nursery &amp; Seed. 
</P>
<P>
Aquasearch will receive a 50.1% interest in the joint venture, to be known as 
Integrated Aquasearch Inc., and will contribute $1.73 million in cash, 
according to a Securities and Exchange Commission filing. Pecoff will 
contribute $868,260 worth of assets. 
</P>
<P>
Aquasearch issued 500,000 of its shares to Pecoff in connection with the joint 
venture. 
</P>
</TEXT>
