<P>
Pick Blue: Douglas K. Baker has been named president and chief executive of 
Pick Blue, an IBM industry reseller in Irvine. He is the former president and 
chief executive of both Basic/Four and Qantel. Before joining Pick Blue, he was 
a consultant for mergers and acquisitions. 
