<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY NEWSMAKERS: WALKER NAMED TO 2 VP POSITIONS AT TOSHIBA AMERICA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Richard H. Walker has been named vice president-general manager of the copier 
products division for Toshiba America Information Systems Inc., Irvine. He was 
also appointed to the newly created position of vice president-corporate 
marketing. 
</P>
<P>
Walker had been vice president-marketing for the office automation group at 
Panasonic Communications &amp; Systems Co. based in Secaucus, N.J. 
</P>
<P>
Before that, he was vice president of operations for a subsidiary of Time Inc. 
Toshiba America manufactures laptop and desktop computers, copiers, facsimile 
systems, electronic-key telephone and PBX systems and cellular mobile phones. 
</P>
</TEXT>
