<P>
Photo, Product design workstation at Micom Simi Valley headquarters. A 
scaled-down Micom is profitable again. ; Photo, Micom President Gilbert Cabral 
at Simi Valley headquarters. TERESA TAMURA / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Worker 
assembles circuit board. Micom makes devices that allow computers to "talk" to 
each other. 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
